         <div class="container clearfix left skinBox"> 
          <h2>Customer Service</h2> 
          <p><strong>Have a problem with your delivery or registering your digital subscription?</strong></p> 
          <p>Call Subscriber Services toll free at (800) 777-8640 or (716) 842-1111 or email <a href="mailto:SubscriberServices@buffnews.com">SubscriberServices@buffnews.com</a>. Manage your subscription <a href="https://services.buffalonews.com/cgi/cgiip.wsc/custservice/web/login.htm" target="_blank">here</a>. </p> 
          <p><strong>Having problems commenting?</strong></p> 
          <p>Our commenting system is handled by Disqus, which is separate from our subscriber log in. You can comment with a Twitter, Facebook, Google Plus or Disqus account. Once registered, simply click one of the four icons under "Connect with" while adding your comment and sign in.</p> 
          <p>If you are still having problems, email <a href="mailto:webmaster@buffnews.com">webmaster@buffnews.com</a> with details of the problem you are experiencing along with your contact information. </p> 
         </div> 
